INTRODUCTION
------------
nn_calc is a four-function arithmetic calculated implemented with an artificial neural
network (ANN) using backpropagation, written in Python. It is being developed with the
intention of exploring the possible uses of ANNs in a variety of different settings.

STRUCTURE
---------
addition_set.py
File containing the training set for addition.

infrastructure.py
Contains support functions for converting between decimal and binary forms, the
interpretation of lists of weights into their thresholded forms, a ranged random
number generator, creating new matrices, and the sigmoid functions for the ANN.

network.py
Contains the Network class

nn_calc.py
Entry point for the program.

train_set_gen.py
Functions for generating training sets.
